               261         If `True` (default), a copy of any coordinate data is
            made.  This                                                         
               262         argument can only be passed in as a keyword argument.
               263     **keyword_args                                           
               264         Other keyword arguments as applicable for            
            user-defined coordinate frames.                                     
               265         Common options include:                              
               266                                                              
               267         ra, dec : angle-like, optional                       
               268             RA and Dec for frames where ``ra`` and ``dec``   
            are keys in the                                                     
               269             frame's ``representation_component_names``,      
